OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778940666
OL,3,CSoaring cost of fish and chips
OL,4,C'unsustainable'
OL,6,FThe cost of fish and chips has almost
OL,7,Fdoubled since 2020, with prices rising
OL,8,Fthe fastest of all takeaway options,
OL,9,Fofficial data has revealed.
OL,11,FA fish supper now costs #11.17 on
OL,12,Faverage, according to the Office for
OL,13,FNational Statistics (ONS), an increase
OL,14,Fof almost a pound in a year.
OL,16,FIn 2020, a portion of fish and chips
OL,17,Fusually cost #6.65. According to the
OL,18,FONS, the UK's national dish jumped 9%
OL,19,Fin just 12 months.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
