PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778940666
OL,3,CSoaring cost of fish and chips
OL,4,C'unsustainable'
OL,6,FThe rise is due to several factors,
OL,7,Fincluding rising energy costs and the
OL,8,Fgrowing price of popular fish,
OL,9,Fincluding cod. The quotas negotiated
OL,10,Fby the UK, EU and Norway mean
OL,11,Ffishermen are allowed to catch 44%
OL,12,Ffewer cod than last year due to due to
OL,13,Foverfishing concerns and fears cod
OL,14,Fstocks are critically low.
OL,16,FFish and chip shop owners have been
OL,17,Fforced to increase their prices to
OL,18,Fconsumers to try to meet their costs,
OL,19,Fbut many are still struggling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778940666
OL,3,CSoaring cost of fish and chips
OL,4,C'unsustainable'
OL,6,FAndrew Crook, The National Federation
OL,7,Fof Fish Friers' president, said the
OL,8,Fprice of cod has doubled, and haddock
OL,9,Fis not far behind.
OL,11,FAlan Richardson, the owner of Zampa
OL,12,FFish wholesalers, which supplies more
OL,13,Fthan 100 businesses across London,
OL,14,Fsaid in recent months the reduced
OL,15,Fsupply has meant cod has been more
OL,16,Fexpensive than lobster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
