FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778940666
OL,3,CSoaring cost of fish and chips
OL,4,C'unsustainable'
OL,6,F"A family of five going out on a
OL,7,FFriday to get their fish and chips,
OL,8,Fthat's going to be #100. That's not
OL,9,Fsustainable, nobody can do that," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"The knock-on effect for fish and chip
OL,13,Fshops is they cannot sustain this kind
OL,14,Fof increase in price," Mr Richardson
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FHuseyin Kanizi, from The Golden Chippy
OL,18,Fin Greenwich, said: "It's very painful
OL,19,Fbecause it's eating away in your
OL,20,Fpocket and your profit margins are
OL,21,Fgoing down big time."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778940666
OL,3,CSoaring cost of fish and chips
OL,4,C'unsustainable'
OL,6,FHe says many of his regulars are now
OL,7,Fonly able to afford to come once a
OL,8,Ffortnight, or split a portion between
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,FWholesalers like Alan Richardson have
OL,12,Fsuggested chippies switch to
OL,13,Falternative white fish such as ling,
OL,14,Fwhich costs just #13 per kilo and has
OL,15,Fa similar texture.
OL,17,F"Fish and chip shops cannot survive
OL,18,Fwith cod and chips, so we have to look
OL,19,Fat alternatives," he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
